    "faq": {
      "howItWorks": "How does DOAPP work?",
      "howItWorksAnswer": "DOAPP connects clients who need services with independent workers. The client posts a job, workers apply with proposals, the client chooses the best profile, and payment is protected on our platform until both parties confirm the work is completed.",
      "moneyProtection": "How is my money protected?",
      "moneyProtectionAnswer": "When you pay for a job, the money is securely held on our platform. It is only released to the worker when both parties confirm the service was completed correctly. If there's a problem, you can open a dispute.",
      "commissions": "How much does DOAPP charge in commission?",
      "commissionsAnswer": "FREE plan: 8% commission. PRO plan ($4,999/month): 3%. SUPER PRO plan ($8,999/month): 1%. The first 1000 users receive 3 free contracts with no commission.",
      "howToPublish": "How do I post a job?",
      "howToPublishAnswer": "Click 'Post a Job' in the top menu. Fill in the title, description, budget, and dates. Then make the publication payment and an administrator will approve your job to make it visible.",
      "howToApply": "How do I apply for a job?",
      "howToApplyAnswer": "Browse available jobs on the main page. When you find one you're interested in, click 'Apply' and send your proposal with a message and suggested price.",
      "howToGetPaid": "How do I get paid for my work?",
      "howToGetPaidAnswer": "When a job is completed, both parties confirm completion. The payment is credited to your DOAPP balance. You can withdraw it to your bank account (CBU) with a minimum of $1,000 ARS.",
      "problemWithJob": "What do I do if there's a problem with a job?",
      "problemWithJobAnswer": "You can open a dispute from the contract detail. An administrator will review the case and make a fair decision based on evidence from both parties. Meanwhile, the money remains held.",
      "confirmationSystem": "How does the confirmation system work?",
      "confirmationSystemAnswer": "When the work is done, both parties must confirm. If one party doesn't confirm within 2 hours, the system automatically confirms and releases the payment."
    }
  },
